metadata.description:
Immerse yourself in the ambient soundscape of Harris Cole's latest creation for hedsTAPE 14. Crafted with meticulous precision using his personal hardware, this LA-based producer invites listeners into a journey through sound.

    This hedsTAPE was curated by Harris Cole during a collaborative production cycle. Each track is accompanied by a visualizer, and the entire mix is included with each mint. The talented artists featured in this mix have been chosen anonymously via heds community curation, and appear in the following order:
        
    Robu
    Allove
    FRESH STUFF
    Dutchyyy
    Floro
    Billings
    Insowmya
    Toha
    Envi
    Athena Yasaman
    
    Find out how to participate @ heds.app
metadata.name: hedsTAPE 14 #1
